#: src/components/pages/PickleballTokyoPage.re.mjs:208
msgid ""
"As mentioned above, public games are not really a thing in Japan. However, "
"you can find some public games on the home page of this website. They will "
"tend to be full with a waitlist so just join the waitlist and cross your "
"fingers. 5-6 spots tend to open up the day of the event as people cancel "
"last minute."
msgstr ""
"如上所述，公开比赛在日本并不常见。但是，您可以在此网站的主页上找到一些公开比"
"赛。它们通常会满员并有等待列表，所以只需加入等待列表并祈祷好运。通常在活动当"
"天会有5-6个位置，因为人们会在最后一分钟取消。"

